OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain soon
OL,6,Fclears Shetland, then a dry evening
OL,7,Fwith clear spells, especially for
OL,8,FOrkney. Turning cloudier overnight
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,10,Fnorthwards. Strong southeasterly winds
OL,11,Fwith risk of coastal gales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA mixed day of sunny spells
OL,14,Fand blustery showers, which may be
OL,15,Fheavy at times. Strong southeasterly
OL,16,Fwinds and risk of coastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
