OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells with a few showers
OL,7,FMonday. Mostly dry with sunny spells
OL,8,Fon Tuesday. Cloudier on Wednesday with
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain. Winds becoming
OL,10,Flight then strengthening on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
